<function>

access:   public

name: linkStylesheet

param: string, $href

param: array, $attribs, NULL

return: string

</function>

Returns a <link rel="stylesheet" ... /> tag.

* Parameters:

 * string //$href//: The source href for the stylesheet.

 * array //$attribs//: Additional attributes for the <link> tag.

* Returns string: The <link ... /> tag.

Returns a <link rel="stylesheet" ... /> tag.